{{!-- Naz: this is the page that appears when the user clicks the "explore" button from the musicians list page
Goals of the page
1) Explore all the information associated with the user
2) Be able to message the user
*3) Perhaps be able to see if he belongs to any bands. If so, click to view the band page --}}

<div class="jumbotron my-3">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <h1><span>{{nickname}}</span></h1>
        <img src="{{avatar}}" width="250px" height="auto">
    </div>
</div>
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row d-flex flex-row justify-content-around">
            <div class="col-md-8 my-5 p-0 border-right text-center">
                <h3>Description</h3>
                <p>{{description}}</p>
                <hr>
                <p></p>
                <h3>Location</h3>
                <h6>City: {{city}}</h6>
                <h6>Province: {{province}}</h6>
                <h6>Postal-code: {{zip}}</h6>
               
                <h2 class="my-5">Would you like to contact {{nickname}} ???</h2>
                <hr class="mb-4">
                    <form class="p-5" action="/members/explore/message/{{UserId}}" method="POST">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Sent by</label>
                            <input type="email" class="form-control" value="{{currentUser.email}}" name="email" readonly>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Enter your message below</label>
                            <textarea class="form-control" name="message" rows="3" aria-label="message"></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Send Message</button>
                    </form>         
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-2 my-2 p-3 border">
               <h3>:) Welcome, </h3><h4> {{currentUser.email}}</h4>
                 <a class="btn btn-outline-danger my-5" href="/logout">
                    Logout
                 <a>
              <h4>Make yourself known with a detailed account!</h4>
              <hr>
                 <a class="btn btn-outline-warning my-5" href="/members/edit/{{currentUser.id}}">
                    Edit Personal Account
                 <a>
                 <a class="btn btn-outline-success my-5" href="/members/{{currentUser.id}}">
                    Create Personal Account
                 <a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
